vida eterna após a morte.

122
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,433
Portanto, entregamos o corpo
do Rei Ecbert,

123
00:13:11,434 --> 00:13:14,867
Rei de Mecia e de Wessex,
Bretwalda,

124
00:13:14,868 --> 00:13:17,467
